org.icepdf.core.pobjects.acroform

Class LockDictionary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.icepdf.core.pobjects.Dictionary
      • org.icepdf.core.pobjects.acroform.LockDictionary

  • public class LockDictionary
extends Dictionary
    The signature field lock dictionary (described in Table 233) contains field names from the signature seed value dictionary (described in Table 234) that cannot be changed through the user interface of a conforming reader.
    Since:
    6.1

    • Field Detail

      • LOCK_TYPE_VALUE

        public static final Name LOCK_TYPE_VALUE
        (Optional) The type of PDF object that this dictionary describes; if present, shall be SigFieldLock for a signature field lock dictionary.

      • ACTION_KEY

        public static final Name ACTION_KEY
        (Required) A name which, in conjunction with Fields, indicates the set of fields that should be locked. The value shall be one of the following:
        • AllAll fields in the document
        • IncludeAll fields specified in Fields
        • ExcludeAll fields except those specified in Fields
